1.title: The Hooker: Part 1
1.plot: The Pilot. When Adam's ex-girlfriend Corri moves back to Holliston, he is devastated to learn that she has a boyfriend (Kevin) who is successful, gorgeous, wealthy, and everything that Adam is not. Adam tries to prove to Corri that he too has moved on.

2.title: The Hooker: Part 2
2.plot: The Pilot continued. Adam follows the horrible advice of his imaginary alien friend Oderus and hires a hooker to pose as his girlfriend on a double date with Corri and Kevin. As the date goes down in flames, Adam calls upon Joe to help get him out of his disastrous situation.

3.title: Camera Rental: Part 1
3.plot: In a plot to raise money for the mock trailer to their soccer zombie movie Shinpads, Adam and Joe rent out the cable company's camera to a stranger... who disappears and does not return it. Meanwhile, Laura and Corri discover that their new apartment is haunted.

4.title: Camera Rental: Part 2
4.plot: Adam and Joe stage a robbery to help explain how they lost the cable company's camera while Corri and Laura plot to get out of their apartment lease.

5.title: Skunked
5.plot: While trying to find Axl the cat, Adam and Joe wind up getting sprayed by a skunk. Corri and Laura race to the local convenient store to find vinegar for the boys, but find themselves detained by the police who are suspicious about their questionable purchase.

6.title: Candyman: Part 1
6.plot: Fanboy dreams come true when legendary genre actor Tony Todd (Candyman) does a special guest appearance on Adam and Joe's cable access show "The Movie Crypt" and then takes the boys out for a wild night on the town. Their dream come true becomes a living nightmare when the eccentric and larger than life actor moves in on their couch and turns their lives upside down. Meanwhile, Corri breaks up with Kevin.

7.title: Candyman: Part 2
7.plot: Tony Todd continues to destroy Adam and Joe's lives by overstaying his welcome and ultimately moving in on the recently single and vulnerable Corri. Adam and Joe stage a plan to murder the arrogant actor and Adam is forced to stand up to the menacing movie star and defend Corri's honor.

8.title: Laura's Little Twitter
8.plot: Laura becomes the most popular girl on Twitter after mistakenly posting a revealing photo of herself. Meanwhile, Adam and Joe hire a schizophrenic make-up effects artist to help them make their mock trailer for Shinpads. To make matters worse, Adam faces a moral dilemma when Corri offers to pose nude for their project.

9.title: Weekend of Horrors: Part 1
9.plot: The gang attends a local horror convention together in an effort to meet Adam and Joe's favorite film director (John Landis) and hand him their mock trailer for Shinpads. When they can't afford a front-of-the-line "gold pass", Joe pretends to be disabled in order to skip the three hour long wait. Meanwhile, Lance is concerned that he may have caught a sexually transmitted disease after sharing a beer with the lead singer of Faster Pussycat.

10.title: Weekend of Horrors: Part 2
10.plot: After managing to do most everything a fan can do wrong at a horror convention and make enemies with such iconic horror stars as Danielle Harris and Kane Hodder, Adam and Joe finally get their mock trailer for Shinpads into the hands of John Landis. When Landis responds to the boys weeks later in the form of a letter, the result is not what the boys were hoping for.

0.title: The Christmas Special
0.plot: When the gang finds themselves trapped in the apartment without power during a Christmas Eve blizzard they reminisce on how they all first met and Adam and Corri's complicated relationship takes an eventful turn. Meanwhile, a deranged serial killer named "the Christine Cringle Tingler" escapes from Framingham Women's State Penitentiary and is on the loose. An hour-long very special episode of Holliston.

1.title: Suicidal Tendencies
1.plot: When Corri discovers that legendary horror icon Kane Hodder is staying in her hospital while recovering from a failed suicide attempt, Adam and Joe hatch a plan to sign him out under their care in order to get him to star in their short film for SHINPADS.

2.title: Halloween Girl
2.plot: When Adam and Joe use Kane Hodder's cell phone contacts to lure scream queen Danielle Harris to Holliston to act in their short film, the diva begins using Adam for money and the painkillers from his recent dental surgery. Meanwhile, the boys obtain a free production intern named Nicolo, a townie from South Boston with a knack for screwing things up.

3.title: Hobgoblin
3.plot: Frustrated with how the SHINPADS short film is going, Joe convinces Adam, Corri, and Laura to head off into the woods for the weekend and shoot a found footage movie to capitalize on the current Hollywood trend. The boys think they've made up the infamous "Holliston Hobgoblin"... but did they?

4.title: Honesty
4.plot: When Laura's judgmental parents visit, a case of mistaken identity has them falling in love with Adam and Joe having to pretend to be his servant. Meanwhile, Corri convinces Adam and Joe to sit down with their childhood bully and help him complete the final step in his rehab program.

5.title: Rock the Cradle
5.plot: Though Corri suspects that Adam's new girlfriend may not be exactly who he thinks she is, everyone else seems to adore her and think that Corri is just jealous. Meanwhile, Lance is paid a visit by a young man claiming to be his illegitimate son.

6.title: Joe's Soda
6.plot: When Corri is bitten by a crazed man at her hospital, Adam and Joe fear she may have been bitten by a werewolf and jump into action to save her, leaving Laura alone to stand guard over her. Meanwhile, Joe makes a compelling case for why his Diet Coke being flat is the more important story line of the episode.

7.title: Blobby
7.plot: In this special animated episode, Laura mixes together some paints she got from Japan and inadvertently creates The Blob. As the creature wreaks havoc on the once peaceful small town of Holliston, Adam and Joe try to capture the events on video in order to make a film that will gain them submission to Fantastic Fest in Austin.

8.title: Cursed
8.plot: When a random fan of Laura's artwork sends her a strange video tape, the gang watches it before realizing that viewing the footage comes with a hefty price. Meanwhile, Adam's latest girlfriend may be the most beautiful girl he's ever seen but he faces a moral dilemma when he realizes that she has one gigantic tragic flaw.

9.title: Kevin's Wedding
9.plot: When Corri gets an invite to her ex-boyfriend Kevin's wedding, she enlists Adam as her date in an effort to make Kevin jealous while Laura uses the evening as an opportunity to drop a bomb of bad news on Joe. Meanwhile, Oderus moves out of Adam's closet after feeling like their friendship is completely one-sided.

10.title: Farm Festival
10.plot: When Adam and Joe's short film for SHINPADS is rejected by every film festival on the planet, the gang holds their own film festival in order to give their work a proper premiere. Joe gives Laura a serious ultimatum, Adam's new girlfriend Dana drops the "L" word on him, Corri shares a personal secret, Lance Rockett debuts his first original music video, Oderus tries to stop Adam from giving up on his dream, and zombies attack the town of Holliston in this epic and heart wrenching special season finale.

imdb.plot outline: The show, based on creator Adam Green's real life and set in his small hometown of Holliston, MA, follows the lives of Adam and Joe, two friends chasing the dream of becoming successful horror movie filmmakers while struggling to make ends meet and dealing with life and the opposite sex in their post-college jobs at a Boston area cable access station where they also host a late night movie program called "The Movie Crypt." The core ensemble is rounded out by Joe's girlfriend Laura (a morbid yet adorable aspiring artist) and Adam's ex-girlfriend and the greatest heartbreak of his life Corri (a gorgeous nurse and aspiring country singer). The other main characters on the show include Adam and Joe's boss Lance Rockett (a cross-dressing 54 year old lead singer for a Van Halen tribute band still living the 80s glam metal lifestyle) and Adam's imaginary friend Oderus Urungus (an alien who lives in his closet and advises him on his life... badly). Often referred to as "Friends" for geeks and "The Big Bang Theory" meets "Evil Dead 2", Holliston is a brilliantly twisted take on the traditional multi-camera sitcom that captures the comedy, the horror, and the heart of the time of life when the struggle to "make it" is really just beginning and nothing is working out like they told you it would.

plot: Two down and out aspiring filmmakers struggle with life, career, and the opposite sex as they attempt to make it out of the small New England town they are trapped in and into the big time.::anonymous
